TT 4416 "Bir bakayim..." VO__AMICIA__CH04__CHATTER__INTERACT_LADDER__010__M__1
TT 4417 "Hm... Evet, ya katran ya hiç..." VO__AMICIA__CH04__CHATTER__INTERACT_LADDER__020__M__1
