TT 8830 "Tabii, hareket edelim." VO__ARNAUD__GENERIC__RESPONSE__FOLLOW__001__M__1
TT 8831 "Tamam, hadi." VO__ARNAUD__GENERIC__RESPONSE__FOLLOW__001__M__2
TT 8832 "Beraber gidelim." VO__ARNAUD__GENERIC__RESPONSE__FOLLOW__001__M__3
