TT 13774 "Evet..." VO__LUCAS__CH01__CHATTER__FIRST_STEPS__030__M__1
TT 13775 "Bir kale..." VO__LUCAS__CH01__CHATTER__FIRST_STEPS__060__M__1
TT 13776 "Evet! Ve seni böcege dönüstürecegim!" VO__LUCAS__CH01__CHATTER__HIDESEEK_BEGIN__020__M__1
TT 13777 "Ona kadar sayacagim! Sonra pesinize düsecegim Kral Hugo ve..." VO__LUCAS__CH01__CHATTER__HIDESEEK_BEGIN__040__M__1
TT 13778 "Peki... O zaman HADI GIDIN!" VO__LUCAS__CH01__CHATTER__HIDESEEK_BEGIN__060__M__1
TT 13779 "Biiir!" VO__LUCAS__CH01__CHATTER__HIDESEEK_COUNTING__010__M__1
TT 13780 "Iki!" VO__LUCAS__CH01__CHATTER__HIDESEEK_COUNTING__020__M__1
TT 13781 "Üç!" VO__LUCAS__CH01__CHATTER__HIDESEEK_COUNTING__030__M__1
TT 13782 "Dört!" VO__LUCAS__CH01__CHATTER__HIDESEEK_COUNTING__040__M__1
TT 13783 "Beees!" VO__LUCAS__CH01__CHATTER__HIDESEEK_COUNTING__050__M__1
TT 13784 "Alti!" VO__LUCAS__CH01__CHATTER__HIDESEEK_COUNTING__060__M__1
TT 13785 "Yedi!" VO__LUCAS__CH01__CHATTER__HIDESEEK_COUNTING__070__M__1
TT 13786 "Sekiz!" VO__LUCAS__CH01__CHATTER__HIDESEEK_COUNTING__080__M__1
TT 13787 "Dokuuuz!" VO__LUCAS__CH01__CHATTER__HIDESEEK_COUNTING__090__M__1
TT 13788 "On!" VO__LUCAS__CH01__CHATTER__HIDESEEK_COUNTING__110__M__1
TT 13789 "Sekiz! Dokuz! On!" VO__LUCAS__CH01__CHATTER__HIDESEEK_COUNTING__115__M__1
TT 13790 "Geliyoruuum!" VO__LUCAS__CH01__CHATTER__HIDESEEK_COUNTING__120__M__1
TT 13791 "Peki o zaman. Neyse, ben simdi çalismaya döneyim." VO__LUCAS__CH01__CHATTER__HIDESEEK_END__010__M__1
TT 13792 "Sey, simyaci olmak istiyorsam..." VO__LUCAS__CH01__CHATTER__HIDESEEK_END__030__M__1
TT 13793 "Aman!" VO__LUCAS__CH01__CHATTER__HIDESEEK_END__040__M__1
TT 13794 "Hâlâ annenin çiragiyim." VO__LUCAS__CH01__CHATTER__HIDESEEK_END__050__M__1
TT 13795 "Tamam! Hosça kalin!" VO__LUCAS__CH01__CHATTER__HIDESEEK_END__080__M__1
TT 13796 "Korku kokusu aliyorum..." VO__LUCAS__CH01__CHATTER__HIDESEEK_ROUND_1__030__M__1
TT 13797 "Ben Lucas, hainlerin haini, ayak parmaklarindan yahni yapmaya yemin ederim! VE ONU YERIM!" VO__LUCAS__CH01__CHATTER__HIDESEEK_ROUND_1__040__M__1
TT 13798 "Neredesiniiiz? Korkunuzun kokusunu aliyorum! Yoksa... kraliyet agiz kokun mu bu?!" VO__LUCAS__CH01__CHATTER__HIDESEEK_ROUND_2__030__M__1
TT 13799 "Bütün krallar düser, Efendim!" VO__LUCAS__CH01__CHATTER__HIDESEEK_ROUND_2__040__M__1
TT 13800 "Çok kolay! O hâlde... sana ikinci bir sans verecegim!" VO__LUCAS__CH01__CHATTER__HIDESEEK_ROUND_2_BEGIN__010__M__1
TT 13801 "Bu sefer merhamet göstermeyecegim! Sana son iyilik kivilcimimi sundum!" VO__LUCAS__CH01__CHATTER__HIDESEEK_ROUND_3__030__M__1
TT 13802 "Aklinizi okuyabiliyorum... Kral Hugo'nun geceleri elma yedigini bile biliyorum!" VO__LUCAS__CH01__CHATTER__HIDESEEK_ROUND_3__040__M__1
TT 13803 "Peki! Kara, kötü kalbim hâlâ avin heyecanindan zevk alabilir... Gidin! Gidin aptallar!" VO__LUCAS__CH01__CHATTER__HIDESEEK_ROUND_3_BEGIN__020__M__1
TT 13804 "Bu sefer sadece bese kadar sayacagim!" VO__LUCAS__CH01__CHATTER__HIDESEEK_ROUND_3_BEGIN__030__M__1
TT 13805 "Bu kale benim!" VO__LUCAS__CH01__CHATTER__HIDESEEK_ROUND_3_LOST__010__M__1
TT 13806 "Birakin onu, lütfen!" VO__LUCAS__CH01__CHATTER__OFFSCREEN_SQUEEZE__030__M__1
TT 13807 "Domuz gibi terliyorum..." VO__LUCAS__CH01__CHATTER__SPRINTING__020__M__1
TT 13808 "Yaniyorum desene!" VO__LUCAS__CH01__CHATTER__SPRINTING__050__M__1
TT 13809 "Ha..." VO__LUCAS__CH01__ONOM__ARRIVAL_RUINS__020__M__1
TT 13810 "Ah!" VO__LUCAS__CH01__ONOM__CART_SQUEEZE_THROUGH__040__M__1
TT 13811 "Onom" VO__LUCAS__CH01__ONOM__HIDESEEK_CHECK_COVER__010__M__1
