TT 14745 "onom" VO__LUCAS__CH05__RTC__195_TROUBLE_ONOM__010__M__1
TT 14746 "Evet... Sanirim kanim dondu... Ama iskalamadigin için tesekkürler... Arenadakilerle ayni gruptandilar, Amicia." VO__LUCAS__CH05__RTC__200_EMBUSH__020__M__1
TT 14747 "Amicia!" VO__LUCAS__CH05__RTC__220_THE_ROPE__010__M__1
TT 14748 "Hugo! Dur!" VO__LUCAS__CH12__CHATTER__CONTROL_LOST__015__M__1
